M: Carbonation is medium. Body is, of course, bone dry, but with plenty of acidity to balance.
O: Extremely drinkable. I compared this side-by-side with Sanctification and found it much more complex, sour, and balanced. Slightly disappointing, since I can find Sanctification much more easily. I guess you really need to let nature do its work without intervening to create a thing of beauty. Get it if and while you can. 1,009 charactersjibbyvonjibb, Apr 07, 2012
